commit.message:
i386: port vxworks to TARGET_CPU_P macro

	PR target/102351

gcc/ChangeLog:

	* config/i386/vxworks.h: Use new macro TARGET_CPU_P.

files.patch:
@@ -73,37 +73,37 @@ along with GCC; see the file COPYING3.  If not see

       if (TARGET_64BIT)					\
 	VX_CPUDEF (X86_64);				\
-      else if (TARGET_PENTIUM4)				\
+      else if (TARGET_CPU_P (PENTIUM4))			\
 	{						\
 	  VX_CPUDEF (PENTIUM4);				\
 	  VX_CPUVDEF (PENTIUM4);			\
